</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns ist von etwievil
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> fürbraht worden, wie in etwievil geschirre auf
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Frawnberg czu Wirczburg
                                <expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgetrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wir
                        den Peter Heydnab, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener, czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> senden, mit
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden davon czu reden. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Symo<ex>n</ex>is</expan> et Jude.</ab>
